":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"[召喚] 簽名師唔該全面進場 (你地自己睇下羞唔羞恥)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800386</a><br />\n<br />\n上水和你shop聽日仲有<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801500</a>"},{"pid":"6fdf79b7034b28f2bd5669798bb1dac357729d53","tid":1801510,"uid":25105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0af68cb227eb07c0fd42c0764abfeb6afc7663fb","tid":1801510,"uid":16465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:39:42.000Z","msg":"推 我都冇咩心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"我明架手足, 時代選中左我地, 生於亂世, 有種責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8278b107255d8c6a6e5fd1e4eac0df979bb5d60","tid":1801510,"uid":146887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2339a9e1e71d012cdeeda2089079b721bf23fec6","tid":1801510,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:47:01.000Z","msg":"明治維新精神領袖<span style=\"color: gold;\">吉田松陰</span>憑藉自己既悉心教導，將知識傳授比長州藩同薩摩藩既下級武士們，最終<span style=\"color: teal;\">細水成百川</span>，武士們促成倒幕大業。"},{"pid":"1aa950bf48dab6b46330a53ea2df4f12c164c373","tid":1801510,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:48:21.000Z","msg":"明治維新精神領袖<span style=\"color: gold;\">吉田松陰</span>憑藉自己既悉心教導，將知識傳授比長州藩同薩摩藩既下級武士們，最終<span style=\"color: teal;\">細水成百川</span>，武士們促成倒幕大業。"},{"pid":"a19d61934d34858a0e7f781d0ddac03cb987ba22","tid":1801510,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:49:13.000Z","msg":"明治維新精神領袖<span style=\"color: gold;\">吉田松陰</span>憑藉自己既悉心教導，將知識傳授比長州藩同薩摩藩既下級武士們，最終<span style=\"color: teal;\">細水成百川</span>，武士們促成倒幕大業。"},{"pid":"ec4a7e0980223f12361e33d4d533c